ygData.messageBody:
I'm a DE Shadowknight and I've been considering trying out the kerra
island fire beetle quest. Have any other DE SKs tried this? I'm
interested in how you were able to get out to Kerra island. I have a
feeling that I'll be KOS in Quenos. Is there a way to get to Kerra
island without going through Quenos? Is there some sort of way through
Quenos similar to the sewers in freeport that is safe for DEs? I'd
love to hear from anyone who's done this.

Thanks,

Atrocity
Bertoxulous
